    <edu:body rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">IIIT-B Library started functioning with a small collection of books donated by the Founder-Director Prof. S. Sadagopan at the ITPL Campus.  The motto of the library is to provide the right information/resource at the right time in the right format to the user. The primary mission of the library is to provide the required educational resources both in print and electronic format for teaching &amp; learning activities, support the academic and research activities of the institution, and to contribute towards fulfilling the vision set by the institute and to extend its reach to the benefit of the lar</edu:body>
