    <edu:url rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI">https://www.iiitb.ac.in/placement-team/roshni-dsouza</edu:url>
    <edu:body rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">roshni [dot] dsouza [at] iiitb [dot] ac [dot] in Roshni DSouza is a leader with 20 years of experience across industry and academia, currently serving as Head – Strategic Partnerships, Alumni Relations, and Career Development (SPARC) at IIIT-Bangalore. She leads corporate partnerships, career development, alumni engagement, learning and development initiatives, training programs, and team management with a focus on building scalable ecosystems that connect students, alumni, and industry. With her expertise as a counselling psychologist, she has been instrumental in designing mentorship frameworks, advancing institutional wellbeing strategies, and developing impact-driven programs that foster student success and professional readiness. At IIIT-B, she has also led portfolios in further educa</edu:body>
    <edu:scrapedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">2026-03-26T19:10:19</edu:scrapedAt>
    <edu:belongsTo rdf:resource="http://semanticweb.iiitb.ac.in/iiitb/IIIT_Bangalore"/>
  </rdf:Description>
