    <edu:body rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">An online Summer School organised by the Centre for Accessibility in the Global South (CAGS), IIIT Bangalore 3:00 pm – 5:00 pm from 24th to 28th June 2024 (Register HERE) Int Advisor Anita Ghai Retired as a dean and professor in School of Human Studies, Ambedkar University Delhi, which she joined in 2015. Before this, Anita has been an associate profess Intern Murali is a fourth-year student at IIIT Bangalore who is passionate about creating meaningful human-centered design solutions. Currently, he is focused on the Digital Societ Intern Third year iM.Tech Computer Science Student at IIIT-Bang</edu:body>
