    <edu:body rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Being a part of Alumni committee helps us to have a close relationship with the Alumni network of IIIT Bangalore. This enables us to learn and grow as individuals with the help of our alumni's The Food committee, is a student organizing committee, acting as a liaison between vendors of all the food services (Mess &amp; Cafeteria) and the student body. Their role is to faithfully represent "Play With Passion" Success comes when you are a good team player and this is truly and sportingly defined by SportsCom, IIIT-B. The committee not only facilitates sportspersons in College Anubhava is the officia</edu:body>
    <edu:scrapedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">2026-03-26T19:08:35</edu:scrapedAt>
