    <edu:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">To be a pioneering force in enhancing communication technologies through cutting-edge translational research, driving innovation, and cultivating a vibrant ecosystem for startups, technology and product development, and talent growth, setting global standards for excellence and impact. COMET Foundation is committed to accelerate the development and deployment of advanced communication technologies Prepare for the next generation of wireless communications for 5G and beyond, through expert-driven research, Consortium based Research, directed research for the specific requirements of Industry, other Govt, verticals and International Collaborative Research Programmes. Collaborate and partner with the Industry both public and private including international collaborations to adopt the technolo</edu:description>
