    <edu:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Bhoomika is a PhD student in Web Science Lab. She holds MTech in Computer Science and Engineering from Visveswaraya Technological University. Prior to joining IIITB she worked as an Assistant Professor at B.M.S college of Engineering and Presidency University, Bangalore with a total 6.5 years of teaching experience. Her areas of interests include Web mining, Semantic Web and Machine Learning. To know more, please visit her LinkedIn profile.</edu:description>
    <edu:belongsTo rdf:resource="http://semanticweb.iiitb.ac.in/iiitb/IIIT_Bangalore"/>
  </rdf:Description>
