    <edu:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Paper titled “Advancing Image Classification through Parameter-Efficient Fine-Tuning: A Study on LoRA with Plant Disease Detection Datasets” accepted at ICLR 2024. Congratulations. Yash Mittal successfully defended his Master of Science (MS) by Research Thesis on “Incremental Learning on Spatial Data and Applications”. Paper titled “Prediction of Transportation Index for Urban Patterns in Small and Medium-sized Indian Cities using Hybrid RidgeGAN Model” accepted in Nature Scientific Reports. Paper weblink :- Van der Pol-informed Neural Networks for Multi-step-ahead Forecasting of Extreme Climatic Events. NeurIPS 2023 – AI4Science. Paper weblink :- Epicasting: An Ensemble Wavelet Neural Network for forecasting epidemics. Neural Networks (2023). Paper weblink :- An ensemble neural network ap</edu:description>
    <edu:belongsTo rdf:resource="http://semanticweb.iiitb.ac.in/iiitb/IIIT_Bangalore"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://semanticweb.iiitb.ac.in/iiitb/lab_VLSI_Systems">
