    <edu:body rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Sign Language Interpreter and Research Associate J D Santhosh is a dedicated Sign Language Interpreter and Research Associate who excels in creating inclusive environments for Pers Post-doctoral fellow at A4I Lab   Carolyn Kavita Tauro is a Post-doctoral fellow at the International Institute of Information Technology (IIIT) Bangalore. Her research interests The consultation, “Re-imagining Pathways for Assistive Technology,” will be a significant step towards creating an inclusive and vibrant AT ecosystem in
India. Sensing Local and CAGS came together and conducted a Hackathon to co-create solu</edu:body>
