    <edu:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Job Description – Architect (Advanced Communication Systems) Job Description – Project Associates Job Description – Business Development Manager Job Description – Program Manager Applications are invited from Indian nationals for the positions of JRF and RA in a IIITB COMET Foundation funded research project on Reconfigurable Intelligent Surfaces (RIS). Interested candidates may forward their application along with detailed resume to comet@iiitb.ac.in. Clearly state the role you are applying for in the subject of your email. Last date to apply: October 20, 2024 Smart Radio Environments: Implementation and deployment for targeted uses-cases. Dr. Priyanka Das Assistant Professor, Department of Electronics and Communication Engineering, IIIT Bangalore, India. Email: priyanka.das@iiitb.ac.in F</edu:description>
    <edu:belongsTo rdf:resource="http://semanticweb.iiitb.ac.in/iiitb/IIIT_Bangalore"/>
  </rdf:Description>
