    <edu:url rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI">https://www.iiitb.ac.in/placement-team/jayachandra-c-m</edu:url>
    <edu:body rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">jayachandra [dot] cm [at] iiitb [dot] ac [dot] in Jayachandra has over 2 year experience in industry. His specialties include relationship management, recruitment, developing marketing plans, and implementing effective advertising strategies to enhance institute - industry relations. Currently, he is an integral part of the placement office, handling the placement process, preparations, career counselling, and more. Prior to joining IIIT-B, He worked with Bionivid Technology Private Limited, Sun Technology Integrators Pvt. Ltd, and Horticulture Department under Government of Karnataka. He has completed his Bachelors in Science (Biotechnology) and Certificate course (Full stack development) in QSpiders training institute Hebbal branch. His interests are reading, music and games.</edu:body>
