    <edu:bio rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Cdr JV Prasad(retd)  has taken over as Executive Officer  (Office of R&amp;D) on 02 Dec19. He has served in Indian Navy for 14 years. He was commissioned into Education branch of Indian Navy  and has held various appointments as Instructor and Technical Officer at various training establishments and selection centres of Indian Navy.</edu:bio>
