    <edu:url rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI">https://www.iiitb.ac.in/events-and-festivals</edu:url>
    <edu:body rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Want to listen to a lecture or music, prove your mettle in debates, have a flare for creative writing, want to showcase your dancing finesse, hone photography skills, master the art of stage performances, there is always something going on. IIIT-B hosts a range of events on the campus round the year. Largely organized and run by academic departments and students, the events provide multiple ways to connect. TEDx talks, hackathons, cultural events, sports events, research showcase events and art competitions are just few to mention, shaping social and intellectual fabric of the campus. Yamini ,</edu:body>
    <edu:scrapedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">2026-03-26T19:08:24</edu:scrapedAt>
    <edu:belongsTo rdf:resource="http://semanticweb.iiitb.ac.in/iiitb/IIIT_Bangalore"/>
  </rdf:Description>
