    <edu:body rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">CAGS hosted a team of students and faculties from the New York University’s Centre for Global Affairs on 15th January 2025 Sensing Local and CAGS came together and conducted a Hackathon to co-create solutions for wayfinding signage for people with vision impairments. Product designers, engineers, softw Sensing Local and CAGS came together and conducted a Hackathon to co-create solutions for wayfinding signage for people with vision impairments. Product designers, engineers, softw</edu:body>
