    <edu:category rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">cags_event</edu:category>
    <edu:publishedDate rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">February 24, 2023</edu:publishedDate>
    <edu:body rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">CAGS hosted a Design Thinking Workshop on 20th January 2023 on accessible education for students with visual impairment to a group of students from New Zealand. Empower – an annual conference bringing together actors in education, technology and organizations working with people with disabilities Read more IIIT Bangalore hosted Shri Ashok Chandra Panda, Hon’ble Minister of Science and Technology of and other officials of Orissa State Government on 12th August 2022 in partnershi A consultative workshop was held on 30th November, 2022 at CAGS-IIITB in collaboration with the Assistive Technology</edu:body>
    <edu:scrapedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">2026-03-26T19:07:31</edu:scrapedAt>
    <edu:belongsTo rdf:resource="http://semanticweb.iiitb.ac.in/iiitb/IIIT_Bangalore"/>
