    <edu:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">International Institute of Information Technology Bangalore The Department of Electronics and Communication Engineering (ECE) at IIIT-Bangalore is a hub of innovation, education, and research focused on shaping the future of electronics and communication technology. Our mission is to create a collaborative learning environment that fosters creativity, critical thinking, and technical expertise, enabling students to thrive in the fast-evolving field of electronics and communication engineering. We are dedicated to delivering comprehensive education, conducting top-quality research, and nurturing partnerships with industry and academia to address societal challenges and advance the frontiers of electronics and communication technology. Abstract: Prof. Kurian, Physical Unclonable Function for</edu:description>
    <edu:belongsTo rdf:resource="http://semanticweb.iiitb.ac.in/iiitb/IIIT_Bangalore"/>
  </rdf:Description>
