    <edu:category rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">cags_event</edu:category>
    <edu:publishedDate rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">April 22, 2025</edu:publishedDate>
    <edu:body rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">The consultation, “Re-imagining Pathways for Assistive Technology,” will be a significant step towards creating an inclusive and vibrant AT ecosystem in
India. CAGS hosted a Design Thinking Workshop on 20th January 2023 on accessible education for students with visual impairment to a group of students from New Zealand.</edu:body>
