    <edu:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Aparna M is a full time MS by Research student at Web Science Lab. She holds a Bachelor’s degree in Information Science engineering from VTU. She has 2 years of work experience in Middleware development for supply chain management. Her areas of interest include Natural Language processing, NLP in Indian and Low-resource languages and Semi-supervised learning. For more, please visit her LinkedIn profile.</edu:description>
