    <edu:url rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI">https://www.iiitb.ac.in/to-recruit-on-campus-pgd-programmes</edu:url>
    <edu:body rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Hire Industry-Ready Talent in Product Designer, User Experience (UX) and Product Management Graduates of the Postgraduate Diploma in Digital Product Design and Management (PGD-DPDM) are trained to bridge technology, user-centered design, and business strategy equipping them to contribute meaningfully from day one. The PGD-DPDM program at IIIT Bangalore develops professionals who can conceptualize, design, and manage digital products end-to-end. Through an interdisciplinary curriculum and hands-on learning, graduates gain the ability to: The cohort represents diverse academic and professional backgrounds , making them effective contributors to dynamic, cross-functional environments. Our graduates are equipped for roles such as: These professionals are skilled in problem framing, user resear</edu:body>
    <edu:scrapedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">2026-03-26T19:08:31</edu:scrapedAt>
    <edu:belongsTo rdf:resource="http://semanticweb.iiitb.ac.in/iiitb/IIIT_Bangalore"/>
  </rdf:Description>
